OL,3,CHegseth makes D-Day speech about
OL,4,C'dangerous ideologies' invading Europe
OL,6,FUS Defence Secretary Pete Hegseth has
OL,7,Fclaimed Europe is being invaded by
OL,8,F"dangerous ideologies" as he made a
OL,9,Fspeech in Normandy to mark the 82nd
OL,10,Fanniversary of D-Day.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the Normandy American
OL,13,FCemetery in Colleville-sur-Mer,
OL,14,Fnorthwestern France, Hegseth claimed
OL,15,Fsome European countries had grown too
OL,16,F"comfortable" with their hard-fought
OL,17,Ffreedoms, and said they "must be
OL,18,Fmaintained".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
