PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780876973
OL,3,CHegseth makes D-Day speech about
OL,4,C'dangerous ideologies' invading Europe
OL,6,FReferencing how the Allied forces
OL,7,Fstormed French beaches in 1944 to
OL,8,Fliberate Nazi-occupied France, Hegseth
OL,9,Fsaid: "Sadly, today, different
OL,10,FEuropean beaches are stormed by
OL,11,Fdifferent dangerous ideologies.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"Beaches in Spain, in Italy, in Greece
OL,19,Fand Bulgaria. Boats and men arrive.
OL,20,FWhen will European capitals do
OL,21,Fsomething about that invasion?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780876973
OL,3,CHegseth makes D-Day speech about
OL,4,C'dangerous ideologies' invading Europe
OL,6,F"The men who fought and died here
OL,7,Frestored freedom to Europe," Hegseth
OL,8,Fcontinued.
OL,10,F"That freedom must be maintained by
OL,11,Fthis generation of leaders and war
OL,12,Ffighters or what they fought for was
OL,13,Fmerely temporary."
OL,15,FHegseth's remarks echoed broader Trump
OL,16,Fadministration criticism of Europe
OL,17,Fover migration, borders and what US
OL,18,Fofficials have described as censorship
OL,19,Fof nationalist and far-right voices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
