OL,3,CHegseth makes D-Day speech about
OL,4,C'dangerous ideologies' invading Europe
OL,6,FOn Saturday, Prime Minister Keir
OL,7,FStarmer's office condemned US Vice
OL,8,FPresident JD Vance for blaming
OL,9,Fimmigration for the killing of 18-year-
OL,10,Fold student Henry Nowak, who was
OL,11,Fstabbed to death in Southampton.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the PM criticised
OL,14,Fpeople for "trying to interfere in our
OL,15,Fdemocracy and seeking to stir up
OL,16,Fdivision on our streets", adding that
OL,17,F"politics should bring people together
OL,18,Feven in the most terrible of
OL,19,Fcircumstances".
OL,26,@vD@LOU
