OL,3,CHegseth makes D-Day speech about
OL,4,C'dangerous ideologies' invading Europe
OL,6,FIn December, the Trump
OL,7,Fadministration's national security
OL,8,Fstrategy warned that Europe faced the
OL,9,F"prospect of civilisational erasure"
OL,10,Fand could become "unrecognisable"
OL,11,Fwithin 20 years - which was rejected
OL,12,Fby EU foreign policy chief Kaja Kallas.
OL,14,F"We are pushing humanity forward,
OL,15,Ftrying to defend human rights and all
OL,16,Fthis, which is actually bringing also
OL,17,Fprosperity for people," Kallas said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@dO]rD@ROUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
