OL,3,CHegseth makes D-Day speech about
OL,4,C'dangerous ideologies' invading Europe
OL,6,FAnti-immigration policy has become a
OL,7,Fkey part of the Trump administration's
OL,8,Fagenda, with Immigration and Customs
OL,9,FEnforcement agency (ICE) agents
OL,10,Farresting thousands of people since
OL,11,FJanuary 2025.
OL,13,FNearly 160,000 Allied troops landed in
OL,14,FNormandy on June 6 1944, to fight Nazi-
OL,15,Foccupied France.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
